    At Prime 94 Steakhouse, we offer a variety of delicious lunch entrees. Our lunch menu includes freshly cooked steaks, juicy burgers, and a selection of premium salads and sandwiches. We also offer a range of side dishes, such as fries, onion rings, mashed potatoes and more. Our lunch menu is available from 11am to 3:30pm daily and offers something for everyone to enjoy. Come by and try one of our delicious lunch options today!

    A steakhouse with a modern twist, this restaurant's menu offers a variety of popular dishes. A variety of steaks and seafood are available, as well as sandwiches, salads and pastas. The bar features an extensive wine list and an excellent selection of scotches, bourbons and whiskeys

    We take the finest PRIME cuts of meat and prepare them in ways you’ve never imagined. When you dine with us, it’s an experience like no other.

    From the bustle of New York City to the quiet, charming life of a small town. That's what you'll find at Prime 94 Steakhouse & Grill! We offer a vast array of food choices with something for everyone’s tastes. From fresh oysters to signature salads and, of course, some of the best prime steaks around!
